{"hdce64937g7265g47edgae77ge31260ba0e67": ["*Ethel grits her teeth - struggling to speak, but the spell holds. She can't answer any more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "d9c4c651-9447-10c1-eae6-8d46e299e948"], "h3c95012eg4f69g423cg920ag4782eb9be451": ["*A charm on the hag's body flashes a faint glow.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "257da951-9161-da12-90f3-8420049d8688"], "h4946bd5ag31b0g4c9cga7e1g5e4ef0f220f5": ["ARGH. You knuckle-dragging gobshite.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "ff09509c-10dd-7e6b-f4d8-f84d6bc471a8"], "hba222055gcb0dg412bgb006g1a7f536b4fd7": ["You will bleed - you will choke on your own <i>guts</i> for this. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "ef63bdce-85f6-ed75-ccfd-f2288563da71"], "hf97395cbg14aag4ffdga76fgc7cea3b400aa": ["You're quite lively for a corpse.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "c9493cb9-2122-f13a-4d1a-7bbae00afa48"], "hb41f9305g8713g4b91g903dg3c4612801ea0": ["I'm a <i>hag</i>, you little snot. I've been ready for death - <i>planning </i>for death - longer than you've been born.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "a14e132a-eaa1-ba40-79b8-a64473e709b2"], "he7505359g34e1g491fg97a6g1179810e3250": ["Tell me the truth - what did you want with Mayrina?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "dd3496a5-2e31-61e2-5f9f-233eb20a2fdf"], "hb0949080gd6ebg4916gb893gec637c9ab26f": ["I didn't want the girl, sweetie. I wanted her <i>babe.</i>", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "ba73f5c1-ad5b-0e50-1449-348133a2e989"], "ha9ff239dg0738g4869g9cfagc34f21b6c12d": ["I would have gobbled it up and given birth to my very own hag daughter.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "10c28abe-a7cf-e22a-0480-b6742521f9cb"], "h6c375715ge3a0g45a8g89dag4c1ba558530e": ["From my guts she would've come - my blood, my <i>bile.</i> It would have been glorious. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "fb688c11-3737-9c1c-513b-13f0059a0966"], "h47744bb8gd554g4332g95aag93514708b19f": ["You're dead and I'm not. Deal with it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "6baa4222-4215-72a8-288d-d8cc1efb0617"], "h5cdb95d2ge7b9g4b9bga25bg22da5a28a90b": ["Oh, you really are thick, you know that? ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "f3d85a52-d673-dec3-2d89-124f39e9125b"], "h565b24c5gf65fg4811gb271g4baf75dd2365": ["I hope that wriggler eats you from the inside out. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "31d210fa-d4da-41d1-8b1a-2e6f473bad7f"], "ha6e46d1ag916dg4cb3g8471gf08c3f294931": ["What deal did you make with Mayrina?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "2547c975-2ab4-98c4-6f91-9aeb8f59be25"], "hf5006b57g3515g495dg9c02g6fba7e6cabc2": ["The brat's husband is <i>dead. </i>So sad. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "e7c5866b-41cc-a21d-4751-f1892bc534a9"], "h7c6b7833gc4c0g487dg9386ge9a61f444dfd": ["She wanted me to bring him back to life. Little fool thought it would fix everything. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "2081cefe-6e6c-0371-0936-90b5b8a8d496"], "h4aee8096g54e9g48a4gbb6dgc845e6cb7d88": ["Do you have any regrets?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "b37a99d1-d6ba-c37e-32fa-d0e48f287eb7"], "hc46c9e80g08b6g40cbgbb75gbaa70808161d": ["Only that I don't get to see the flesh melt from your bones, your guts dissolve, and your brain <i>liquefy </i>as you turn into a mind flayer.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "35228889-9663-5646-2823-1b16020607e9"], "hf5f799fdg4833g4187g9e68g8688a5948700": ["You'll weep, you'll beg, you'll plead - anything to make it stop.  And once you stand tall, proud and tentacled? ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "640e2fef-ad36-6063-42dc-5eaf16a0c1ad"], "h6460f8d3g763bg427bgabf1gf82e3d508c8d": ["You'll butcher your friends and your loved ones LIKE THE ILLTHID SCUM YOU ARE.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "57c304cc-0137-eefc-ff64-15001770624b"], "h3dfe12e6g729cg486dg9d4fg06cd61127670": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "cb8b8645-fa2f-1079-cb37-93c15e8253e5"], "h5eeb9f23g7bfcg4c99g84efg1da9748b2d5c": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "14740286-6a3b-8724-4652-ddab51a59686"], "h6fe54613g03b7g4086g9931gb4a276953035": ["Bleed... choke on... your guts...", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "536b111a-6498-3034-9c22-e3c1230bb856"], "hd2ab67c1gc826g4597gb9dcg3ccaf740094e": ["Why did you want Mayrina?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "9254fa97-85e5-8dcd-24d1-e01806f1f622"], "hb9518a1fgc9b9g4a2dga5b1ge46ce6c2dbb9": ["Didn't want... the girl... wanted her... <i>babe. </i>", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "fe72219a-feee-f9bb-bcd7-0e769a6108f8"], "h78ead6a1gfbb8g48e3gae1egaa7457f80266": ["... was going to... eat it... and make a... hag daughter...", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "f3590626-1db6-fdb9-5da4-c8ea783922fd"], "hb2a837e7gdbdcg44e2ga047g860920afe3f5": ["Are you the only hag around here?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "feaf130c-5348-34dc-3ac2-a7ac03c2ecc0"], "hb74d7b62g7077g400bg9d3eg3bf99a0f0a91": ["Where there's people... there's... hags.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "9dd3c5e8-1874-df2c-50f8-66195d4b2aeb"], "h0ece3ee2g895fg40abg90eeg39116b29a582": ["Where do you keep your valuables?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "1e67f6ad-1431-8618-f233-967b0d03f4a7"], "h2e47612ag4279g44f5g9129gabcdfd33da44": ["In my... workroom...", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "a3c872b4-3846-4a88-ab15-30ac76b0b65f"], "hf8f15ed4ga8f7g440bga52eg88ba6ef733f6": ["Why are you so cruel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "df512a50-2e9c-b96a-93e8-3e910f7c751c"], "h3bc06196gaae4g45aag8dafg23b6ac58fa64": ["Not me.... that's cruel. It's... people. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "90bbc250-d96f-a8c0-72f3-e3df7d0f4052"], "hc860c219g2cf2g46c6gad73g9177c52ab06c": ["They want... and want... and want. I merely... give. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "cd111bdb-1f05-cb4b-482a-d91767dc87f4"], "h648e3660gaddbg4796gac16ge74b952463d0": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "f38bde12-8694-b71b-2a7f-df781eff9ebc"], "he72fd2c9g6e63g4ef1g814dga1f7092b3b46": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "a23a205e-4efd-a841-20b6-493308ccc616"], "h74b6385eg7bc5g4f5ag8b67g49a30dc75584": ["ARGH. Where is the knuckle-dragging gobshite that killed me? ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "7d412946-d213-7cea-0a77-cf8d121dd040"], "h491fd46dg4d81g4d50ga810gb80cd1196757": ["Does being dead bother you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "5c267903-2434-db9d-6856-1ecd8b8b843a"], "he19b41e0g1f7ag4bd3ga642g45f9352022e5": ["You think is the first time? I'll find a way back. I swear it. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "2aaa1163-7286-2c77-f37f-052eea857e7e"], "h00b926f4g002fg4c9fgbc47g19ce43872253": ["And then I will make the cretin beg, plead, <i>weep </i>for what will always be denied... ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "3b84411a-868f-85ff-383f-70d04a5bad24"], "h16d4e03bg6703g4d53g930agc97c1c789aac": [" ... the sweet release of death. ", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "47a12a31-8e69-bc57-bb29-ac8fa94416b1"], "h255ea67ag90eeg476bg9f72g738a4a24b0c2": ["Why are you so cruel?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "a13f5ca8-54ec-6d2c-9363-60b14c1204aa"], "hc558c863g5270g4a2bg84c3ge3073471d347": ["Please. It's you lot who come to me. All you do is <i>want</i> - to be prettier, to be richer, to be loved.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "5e8a8979-4fde-c0ae-835c-ca3b5c3c1fc7"], "ha3f13b86g0e41g425fg92e8ga1c5a718014e": ["People are their own worst enemies, petal. I just let them see it.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "ef6750bc-30f0-2b31-e54d-450c2d7c64a3"], "h774d263bg5651g4f08ga5ebg81ee76db2f42": ["Do you have any regrets?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "2aaad13d-584c-ac81-cc11-f98b9cda3470"], "h4cd654abg045bg4129ga4bag0d5a22aa4c90": ["Only one.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "9ca3c28b-6ea8-0fc8-f086-fb07f0d0bfa2"], "h66048d35g8a5ag401dg9b79ga995b2d9acc4": ["And you'll never know.", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "87a90da2-5c7c-3aa9-d595-0f563a9a86c4"], "ha30e054agca0bg4d03g9d9fg3b13ff125715": ["Kill them... kill them... all...", "c6ef4eea-fd50-2b8a-41c8-0fdbad366d67", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Swamp\\HAG_Hag_Dead.html", "5fc3ff03-16da-9572-a147-f6787ec9e281"]}